{"ts":"2026-07-06T21:58:30.613Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"Domain-by-domain SDK promotion under pm-usfg covers read (pm-rjqr), lifecycle (pm-98cz), schema/config/profile (pm-3mna), history maintenance (pm-4a7m), plan (pm-je50), governance/health/gc (pm-oxrw), annotations (pm-zwpp), and execution (pm-oslr) — but nobody owns the package/extension platform family. The universal-tool story (pm-w89s, exemplar pm-cbwg) requires an SDK-built PM tool to install and manage packages without shelling to the CLI. Promote the install/upgrade/extension lifecycle logic (multi-target install aggregation, managed-extensions.json state, activation) behind typed SDK primitives, and align with the CLI-side consolidation pm-tnud so the noun rename and the SDK promotion do not conflict."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-x6jf"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Promote package & extension lifecycle primitives to the public SDK: install, upgrade, extension list/enable/disable, managed-package state"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":""},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Feature"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["architecture","area:extensions","area:sdk"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-06T21:58:30.613Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-06T21:58:30.613Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":480},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"SDK exports typed primitives for package install/upgrade and extension lifecycle (list, enable/disable, managed-extensions state) returning the same structured results the CLI renders; pm install/upgrade/extension/package commands consume only these primitives; docstrings + linked tests + SDK reference docs; zero behavior change (install/extension specs green)"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-usfg"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"medium"}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"f330054fb9abee8a0d98118a514d7ea2d433cd8d4aed625c5c8b2e554e16d265","message":""}
