{"ts":"2026-07-14T18:05:32.056Z","author":"codex-root","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/15","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-14T18:05:32.055Z","author":"codex-root","text":"Observability evidence: packed-package execution produced healthy local telemetry configuration and pm health warning_count=0. Live Sentry query found zero criticals and two actionable highs, both pre-existing external-extension issues already tracked by open/unclaimed pm-d4ns (PM-CLI-2B, one handled event on 2026.7.11) and pm-7n5a (PM-CLI-29); 17 expected handled events were filtered. Trace/log lists had no 24h/1h rows, so real-time transaction/log ingestion is not claimed."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-14T18:05:32.056Z"}],"before_hash":"6901b1c1c67213555395b1eb99663fe3cf9599f431a21557866af8952ae104d7","after_hash":"301bc291a66cde8e32b1922a724297be712b5611c42aad182b0bf75ea69e9a52"}
{"ts":"2026-07-14T18:08:01.632Z","author":"codex-root","op":"learning_add","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-14T18:08:01.632Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/learnings","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-14T18:08:01.631Z","author":"codex-root","text":"Dynamic extension list flags cross two parsers: Commander consumes declared options before loose argv reconciliation, so an empty loose-occurrence ledger must preserve Commander values rather than replace them. Public output ownership should use a structural marker so independently installed packages do not depend on shared class identity."}]}],"before_hash":"301bc291a66cde8e32b1922a724297be712b5611c42aad182b0bf75ea69e9a52","after_hash":"a3e53c68a2a04989fc434fe0d852a2da594c1a8bb757d45272cfe0ece5aadd4a"}
{"ts":"2026-07-14T18:08:26.930Z","author":"codex-root","op":"update","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-14T18:08:26.930Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/resolution","value":"Completed the public package lifecycle family and its remaining dynamic host contracts across SDK, CLI, tests, and author documentation."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/expected_result","value":"Custom PM tools and packages manage lifecycle and own dynamic command input/output through typed public SDK primitives."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/actual_result","value":"Lifecycle primitives were previously promoted incrementally while the remaining list parsing, output ownership, renderer parity, and passthrough contracts lacked a complete verified boundary."}],"before_hash":"a3e53c68a2a04989fc434fe0d852a2da594c1a8bb757d45272cfe0ece5aadd4a","after_hash":"7d12064b111910e0664d6d70f628d86781e7d8ab8c154c61c61b9c4ae1cff062","message":"Record completed package lifecycle feature family"}
