{"ts":"2026-07-14T18:22:33.141Z","author":"codex-root","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/16","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-14T18:22:33.141Z","author":"codex-root","text":"PR #561 review pass 1: Greptile correctly identified scalar Commander accumulator hardening and structural-marker collision risk; CodeRabbit correctly identified missing CHANGELOG.md pm docs links. The fix accepts scalar-or-array previous values, uses a collision-resistant versioned protocol value, adds regression assertions, and links CHANGELOG.md to all five represented items. Gemini, Sourcery, and CodeRabbit full-review capacity notices were external quota limits, not code findings."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-14T18:22:33.141Z"}],"before_hash":"f88f2964a73458930c4ed577a4bb3dcb60817eab6d0451940a8e06392a55e9b2","after_hash":"1f2f4ea0d89d215bc2a327e59844fa86b099b77b550c537a43a633588c23055a"}
